title: $2000 / 3br - MARSHFIELD OCEAN FRONT WINTER RENTAL
posting_body: ['AVAILABLE OCTOBER 1, 2022: This one floor spacious oceanfront home features three bedrooms and a full bath.', 'The open floor plan incorporates the eat-in kitchen into the living room and out into the Great Room with the million dollar ocean views This front room features 35 feet of spectacular, sweeping North Atlantic Ocean views!', 'The kitchen is fully featured appliance-wise.', 'Verizon FiOS HDTV, internet, and landline phone IS INCLUDED IN THE MONTHLY RENT!!!.', 'There is a full size clothes washer and dryer for your use as well.', 'Living in this home for the eight months will provide some fantastic memories of a fall, winter, and spring spent on the coast!', '* Lease Term: October 1, 2022 - May 26, 2023', '* Maximum occupancy is 5 based on bedroom configuration below', '* Master Bedroom has a queen bed, Bedroom 2 has 1 twin bed, Bedroom 3 has 2 twin beds', '*', 'No smoking indoors', '* NO PETS', '* No groups or subletting allowed', '* Verification of employment/source of funds, credit rating, and references will be obtained', '* Initial payment of $ 5733.00 (First/Last/Security Deposit of $ 2000.00)', '* Owner pays HDTV, High Speed Internet, and Landline Phone, RE taxes, water, sewer, and trash municipal utilities', "* Electric and Gas utilities are tenant's responsibility.", "* Waterfront living on Marshfield's finest beach!", 'This is a PTRT Managed Property']
